<SLUG> BC-HKN-COYOTES-SENATORS-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
COYOTES, KHABIBULIN GET SWEET REVENGE 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By BOB MCMANAMAN  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
