u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-MIDEAST-HNS &LR;      12-13 0051
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CLINTON-MIDEAST-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  Sunday, December 13, 1998
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
Editors: &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
CLINTON-MIDEAST(Jersusalem) _ A story will move at 9 p.m., CDT,
Sunday. By NANCY MATHIS. Questions, call Jake Doherty at
713-220-7674. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Houston Chronicle  &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
