<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-13 20:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7592 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-IRELAND-NEU     12-13 0035
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-IRELAND-NEUTRALITY-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   IRELAND-NEUTRALITY (Dublin) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Dec. 13.
