<SLUG> BC-CLINTON-MIDEAST-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`NO ALTERNATIVE' TO PEACE, CLINTON TELLS YOUNG 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and i coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By CHARLES M. SENNOTT  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
